content.webTitle: CD: Rock review: Eugene Mcguinness, Eugene McGuinness

fields.headline: Rock review: Eugene Mcguinness, Eugene McGuinness
fields.bodyText: It's busily eclectic but the first proper album by the Liverpool-based singer-songwriter – whose mini-album last year excited rave reviews – can make no great claims to originality. But what the 22-year-old does with his whimsical art rock influences is less predictable; the arrangements take the songs in odd directions, piquing interest even when the genre experiments drag.
